  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub — the renders folder has 56 finished\n     clips, so there's a LOT more to pull from. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">3Blue1Brown-style animated explainers of the I Ching — the 64 hexagrams, the binary structure Leibniz saw in them, the coin-toss probabilities — rendered as precise mathematical motion graphics in the vulpes monochrome palette with Manim.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The full grid of 64 hexagrams\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/hexagram/grid.jpg\" alt=\"The full grid of 64 hexagrams\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/hexagram/grid.jpg 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/hexagram/grid.jpg 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/hexagram/grid.jpg 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/hexagram/grid.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The full grid of 64 hexagrams\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"854×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A hexagram built line by line — the loom\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/hexagram/loom.jpg\" alt=\"A hexagram built line by line — the loom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/hexagram/loom.jpg 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/hexagram/loom.jpg 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ej